Homework 02: Text Concordance 
~~~~

  Given a directory of clean XHTML documents (e.g. 
  the sample output data from {{{./hw01_tidy.html}Homework 01}}), 
  build a concordance for them - i.e. 
  a database application, which is displayed as 
  a page consisting of 3 sections, showing the alphabet letters
  in the above screen section, all word forms in the left frame and 
  all environments for the given word in the right frame. 
  
  
